msgid "Automatically syncs the active Polylang language with any Trustindex Reviews widget (Airbnb, Google, Booking, Tripadvisor, Yelp and more), so that all widget texts are always displayed in the language the visitor is browsing in — no manual configuration needed."
msgstr "Samodejno sinhronizira aktivni jezik Polylang s katerim koli gradnikom za ocene Trustindex — ročna konfiguracija ni potrebna."
